## Key URLs

- Activity: `https://substack.com/activity` | Profile: `{{profile_url}}`
- Post comments: `{post_url}/comments` | Search: `https://substack.com/search/{query}`

## Key Selectors

- Comment textarea: `textarea[name="body"]` | Note editor: `div[contenteditable="true"]`
- Submit: button text "Post" | Like: `aria-label="Like (N)"` / "Unlike"
- Subscribe: button text "Subscribe" | Threaded reply: `button[aria-label="Comment"]`
- Class names are unreliable (pencraft framework, dynamic). Use `aria-label`, button text, `name` attr.
